runatime/tools/performance_tester.runa
Performance Testing and Benchmarking System

This module provides comprehensive performance testing functionality including:
- Automated performance regression testing
- Benchmark suite execution and analysis
- Load testing and stress testing capabilities
- Performance baseline establishment and comparison
- Micro-benchmark generation and execution
- Performance metrics collection and validation
- Test result analysis and reporting
- Performance threshold validation and alerting
- Integration with CI/CD pipelines for automated testing
- Cross-platform performance comparison
- Performance test case generation and management
- Resource usage validation during testing
- Performance trend analysis and forecasting
- Integration with AOTT system for optimization validation
:End Note

